Dataset Description

The dataset represents an e-commerce system with three main tables:

1. Orders

* order_id: Unique order identifier
* user_id: Customer ID
* product_id: Product ID
* amount: Order value
* order_date: Date of purchase

 2. Users

* user_id: Unique customer ID
* signup_date: Date user joined
* region: Customer location

3. Products

* product_id: Unique product ID
* category: Product category
* price: Product price

These tables simulate a real-world transactional database.
